query:
WITH entities AS (
            SELECT *
            FROM core_liquidations
            WHERE credit_facility_id = $1
              AND completed = false
            ) SELECT i.id AS "entity_id: Repo__Id", e.sequence, e.event, CASE WHEN $2 THEN e.context ELSE NULL::jsonb END as "context: es_entity::ContextData", e.recorded_at FROM entities i JOIN core_liquidation_events e ON i.id = e.id ORDER BY i.id, e.sequence
